#

Beef Tenderloin Steak with Garlic Butter

25 min
$25
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

BeefSteakQuickEasy

Description

Juicy beef tenderloin steaks seared to perfection and topped with rich garlic butter for a mouthwatering experience.

Ingredients

  • beef tenderloin steak: 2 (6 oz each)
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped (optional)
